表的检验约束名称系统-管理员(OK)

CKT_SYS_ADMIN

%RULES%


表的代码预览系统-管理员(OK)

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('sys_admin')
and type = 'U')
drop table sys_admin
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sys_admin */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sys_admin (
AdminID int identity(1,1),
Nick nvarchar(10) null default '',
LoginName nvarchar(20) null default '',
Password nvarchar(50) null default '',
Telephone nvarchar(20) null,
Mobile nvarchar(20) null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
Isdel bit not null default 0,
HeadPicURL nvarchar(50) null,
depotID int null,
IsPDAUser int null,
constraint PK_SYS_ADMIN primary key (AdminID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('sys_admin') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_admin'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'系统-管理员(OK)',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_admin'
go
